'''Vidge-Ribu''' was the largest settlement of the [[Moon/Legends|moon]] [[Lamus]]. It was a small, low-tech [[Farm/Legends|agarian]] community of about 1500 people. Only a few kilometers from the city was the [[Wellspring (Lamus)|Wellspring]].

